-- Security properties
----------------------------------------------------------------------

-- (no security requirements provided)


----------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Whole-model verification summary
----------------------------------------------------------------------

-- Summary 1: Fixed mapping: Write permission = arrival, Read permission = departure
-- Summary 2: Corrected test scenarios to assert arrival precedes departure (op_arr.post = op_dep.pre)
-- Summary 3: Removed contradictory fact nfr_fact_maintainability_no_cycles (conflicted with owner_always_accessible)
-- Summary 4: Removed over-constraining NFR facts not required by the specification
-- Assumption 1: Write permission models arrival slot requests; Read permission models departure slot requests
-- Assumption 2: A Resource represents a time period / slot; sharing a target indicates same time period
-- Assumption 3: Operation pre/post states capture temporal ordering: op_arr.post = op_dep.pre means arrival completes before departure starts
-- Open issue 1: No direct modeling of slot allocation process beyond permission-based operations; may need finer granularity for real-world validation


